This NDA is with Enron Corp. and EBS is not permitted to bind Enron Corp.  
The legal department would like for all potential clients to review our form 
for execution.  If they present their own form we are happy to review it, 
however there is almost always terms of their form that need to be 
negotiated.  Therefore, if they review our form NDA and it is acceptable the 
process is a lot quicker.  

Attached is the NDA with EBS and C-Store Matrix to send to them for 
execution.   Please select the "Read Only" option in order to open and 
print.  Please print 2 originals for signature so each party has an original 
executed NDA, or you may e-mail it to them as long as they follow up with 2 
originals.  After the other party executes it, you will need to get an EBS 
attorney to initial it before an EBS VP or above can execute it on our 
behalf.  If you have any questions please call me and please make sure I get 
an executed original back.  Thanks.

